<add><ab facs="#facs_135_r1l4">dıe Jm ʒu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſten </ab></add> <expan>d<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dıe 
<del rend="strikethrough"> Er </del> mit tür vnd </ab><ab facs="#facs_135_r1l6">tör beſlieſʒ / vnd der </ab><ab facs="#facs_135_r1l7">mit <expan>ſeıne<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vett<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>hanſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_135_r1l8">in geteilter hab ſicʒ </ab></add> etvvieuil Rẏnder vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_135_r2l5">hab <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd cʒum Rotenpühel <expan>getrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
