<ab facs="#facs_135_r2l7"><expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> Armenleuten <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ire Rınder </ab>
