</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_135" id="66r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Aufsesz </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, uns hat
                                <expan>furg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Hans
                            <expan>Wildenstein<ex>er</ex></expan> der jünger,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        nehst den Kynern czum Pernhof, <add>seinen
                                <expan>armenleute<ex>n</ex></expan>, <add>die im zu
                                        <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sten,</add>
<expan>d<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die mit tür und tör besliesz und der mit
                                    <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vett<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Hanse<ex>n</ex></expan> in geteilter hab sicz</add>, etwievil
                        rynder und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ir hab
                            <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> und czum Rotenpühel
                                <expan>getrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> und bestellen wöllet, daz des
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>, armenleuten
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ire rinder und habe wider werden. Auch
                        hat uns derselb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> gesagt, wie daz er vor ew und den
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>unsich<ex>er</ex></expan> sey und doch niht wisz, daz er mit euch
                        ichts czu <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> hab
                                <add><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> lieb und gut</add>. Begern wir von
                        euch, daz ir den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, sichern wöllet auf
                                <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> reht. Das
                            <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und het <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        ir <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dhein<ex>er</ex></expan> der <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> czu im icht
                                <expan>czusprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir euch oder <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheinb<ex>oten</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt
                            <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>cz<ex>ogen</ex></expan> sleunigs
                                <expan>reht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> wir des
                        ermandt <expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan>, so <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>anh<ex>eim</ex></expan> ist; und lat uns des
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>euntlich</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>s<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> bey <expan>dis<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>bot<ex>en</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                                <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>e</expan> Katherine anno viii<hi rend="sup">vo </hi>.</ab>
</div>
